title: Supercars Videos - Drag Races and Tests
description:
Videos from 2013 - 2014, of tests and drag races between the worlds fastest and most expensive super cars.

Bugatti Veyron, Lamborghini Aventador, Hennessey Venom GT, Ferrari F12, Nissan GT-R, Audi R8 V10,
Chevrolet Corvette C7, Porsche 918 Spyder, Mercedes C63 AMG, McLaren MP4-12C, and more...

13 clips in 720p HD quality. Video format: MP4, Size: 1280x720p, Bitrate: 1500-3000 kbps.
